OL,8,GHow could we not show this? Do we even
OL,9,Gneed to write this blurb? Legendary
OL,10,Ghacker Zero Cool and his friends have
OL,11,Gbeen framed by The Plague, who has
OL,12,Gunleashed a computer virus that could
OL,13,Gcause an environmental disaster.
OL,14,GPursued by the Secret Service, the
OL,15,Ggang try to gather the evidence to
OL,16,Gtake The Plague down and stop the
OL,17,Gvirus from unleashing havoc. A
OL,18,Gbumper-fest of hacking, car chases and
OL,19,Gdouble-crossing that has become lore
OL,20,Gin geek culture. Endlessly quotable
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
